</h3><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-118_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-bc7119b7-75b0-4679-ae84-3f4e4c5e28ff"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">There are numerous ways to contribute to the goals of the International Day of Education 2025:
</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dhFVuh gFqzWs pf-121_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-122_"><strong>Raise awareness</strong> - Share this year’s theme and key messages on social media platforms to encourage meaningful conversations.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-124_"><strong>Participate in events</strong> - Join discussions, webinars, and workshops by UNESCO and other educational bodies.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-126_"><strong>Promote digital literacy</strong> - Advocate for training programmes that equip learners and educators with the skills to navigate AI tools effectively.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-128_"><strong>Invest in education</strong> - Support initiatives to provide access to quality education in underserved communities.
</li></ul><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-130_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-a1a71364-1fe7-4b50-9402-d4d172b52340"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Every action counts in building an inclusive, equitable future for education. Whether as an individual, organisation, or policymaker, your contribution can make a difference.
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-133_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-134_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-135_">Conclusion</h3><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-137_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-2d52d86a-af10-478e-afb0-ee6af2453b99"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">The International Day of Education 2025 serves as a reminder of the transformative power of education in shaping a sustainable future. By embracing AI with a focus on human agency, we can ensure that no learner is left behind. Let’s work together to create an education system that empowers individuals, protects their rights, and prepares them for a world where technology and humanity coexist harmoniously.
